b[92C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[m\u001b[1mHomepage\u001b[22m\u001b[10X\u001b[38;5;99m\u001b[4m\u001b[10Chttps://gitforwindows.org/\u001b[m\u001b[69X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[69C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[m\u001b[1mTags\u001b[22m              git, vcs\u001b[87X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[87C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[m\u001b[1mCopyright\u001b[22m         Copyright (C) 1989, 1991 Free Software Foundation, Inc.\u001b[40X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[40C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā                                                                                                                    ‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[m\u001b[1mDescription\u001b[22m\u001b[102X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[102C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[mGit is a free and open source distributed version control system designed to handle everything from small to     \u001b[38;5;212m‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā \u001b[mvery large projects with speed and efficiency.\u001b[69X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[69C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[mGit for Windows focuses on offering a lightweight, native set of tools that bring the full feature set of the    \u001b[38;5;212m‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā \u001b[mGit SCM to Windows while providing appropriate user interfaces for experienced Git users and novices alike.        \u001b[38;5;212m‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā                                                                                                                    ‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[m\u001b[1mRelease Notes\u001b[22m\u001b[100X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[100C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[mChanges since Git for Windows v2.53.0 (February 2nd 2026)\u001b[56X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[56C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[mThis is a security fix release, addressing CVE-2025-66413.\u001b[55X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[55C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[m- CVE-2025-66413, Git for Windows: When a user clones a repository from an attacker-controlled server, Git may   \u001b[38;5;212m‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā \u001b[mattempt NTLM authentication and disclose the user's NTLMv2 hash to the remote server. Since NTLM hashing is weak,  \u001b[38;5;212m‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā \u001b[mthe captured hash can potentially be brute-forced to recover the user's credentials. This is addressed by\u001b[10X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[10C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā \u001b[mdisabling NTLM authentication by default.\u001b[74X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[74C‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā                                                                                                                    ‚Ēā  \r\n‚Ēā   \u001b[38;5;240m‚ÜĎ‚Üď scroll ‚ÄĘ o open homepage ‚ÄĘ esc close\u001b[74X\u001b[38;5;212m\u001b[74C‚Ēā  \r\n‚ēį‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ēĮ  "]
